The screenshot format to use when taking screenshots. This is a client-setting only.

Explanation of values:
* <empty> - The screenshot is saved as a bitmap image.
* bmp - The screenshot is saved as in the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bitmap Bitmap] format.
* png - The screenshot is saved as in the [http://www.libpng.org/pub/png/ Portable Network Graphics] format. This is only available if zlib and libpng support have been compiled in.
* pcx - The screenshot is saved as in [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PCX ZSoft Paintbrush] format.

If an invalid option is supplied the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bitmap Bitmap] format will be used.


'''Valid options:''' [ <empty> | bmp | png | pcx ]

'''Default:''' <empty>